{"tid":2404740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我排隊俾女神同條仔食飯...","createTime":"2021-02-12T02:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T02:15:02.000Z","uid":392019,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"86a4d95133063c57b4db069358e3023dd677f628","tid":2404740,"uid":392019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:05:37.000Z","msg":"自從停學之後好耐都無見過女神，前日佢忽然問我Lunch一唔一齊食好西，仲叫我去拎位先。<br />\n去到先知，原來Walkin都要排個幾鐘。差唔多夠鐘叫女神落樓，點知佢話佢帶埋男朋友嚟，而我從來未聽過佢有男朋友... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最慘係同個reception講轉三個人，點知限聚令原來最多兩個人一張枱，呢個時段available嘅兩張枱仲分到好遠... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後我排咗個幾鐘就係自己一個食，同埋望住隔十幾米嘅女神同佢條新仔食... <br />\n之後女神話唔該我，仲話唔好意思用咗我時間，叫我食完唔洗等埋佢哋兩個... <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1669c490793797a259a6c0e8120bbab597cd27","tid":2404740,"uid":176905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:08:06.000Z","msg":"雖然無是咁的，不過寫得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e45dd1a27f2d97c3db8a62e01d3cfbe10fd3e2","tid":2404740,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:15:02.000Z","msg":"邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n劉明睇殖入式廣告"}]}